(firstQuint)Long Term Integrity Follow-up Evaluation.

 There are few prospective long term follow-up studies on implanted cardiac device (pacemaker/implantable cardioverter defibrillator (ICD)) survivability.

 This study will evaluate the long term performance (5 years) of the transvenous defibrillation leads (ENDOTAK ENDURANCE EZ and teh ENDOTAK RELIANCE.

 Data will be collected at implant, 1 and 6 months, 1,3 and 5 years.

